# Intentionally left without key=value entries.
#
# Cloudflare's Deploy to Cloudflare flow reads `.env.example` and turns any
# assignments here into deploy-time secret prompts. The default YAOS flow
# should start unclaimed, so this file stays blank.
#
# For local development, pass overrides directly when needed:
#   npm run dev -- --var SYNC_TOKEN:dev-sync-token
#
# Attachments and snapshots stay disabled until you add an R2 binding named
# `YAOS_BUCKET` in the Cloudflare dashboard.
